        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "O for a closer walk with God,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "A calm and heavenly frame,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "A light to shine upon the road"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "That leads me to the Lamb!"
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Return, O holy Dove, return,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Sweet messenger of rest!"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "I hate the sins that made Thee mourn"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "And drove Thee from my breast."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "What peaceful hours I once enjoyed!"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "How sweet their memory still!"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "But they have left an aching void"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "The world can never fill."
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "The dearest idol I have known,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "What-eâ€™er that idol be,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Help me to tear it from Thy throne,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "And worship only Thee."
        }
      ],
      "number": 4
    }
  ],
  "title": "O for a Closer Walk!"
